title: Cao Chuan Vegetarian and Beer House
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Western, Beer/Wine
description: 草串蔬食小酒館, at 台北市文山區試院路152號之3, is a small vegetarian eatery that serves light snacks such as skewers, sandwiches, and hot dogs alongside coffee and beer. Alternative atmosphere, hosts live music. Opened since Aug 2014. Note: reported easily missed so look for it.
